# Sync Instructions for Notebook

## 1. Install Git
If you haven't already, install Git on your notebook.

## 2. Clone the Repository
Open a terminal (PowerShell or Command Prompt) on your notebook and run:

```powershell
cd C:\Users\YOUR_USER\
# Backup existing .gemini if it exists
ren .gemini .gemini.bak
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/RatitaVeloz/Gemeni-Sync.git .gemini
```

## 3. Restore Credentials (IMPORTANT)
The [oauth_creds.json](file:///C:/Users/tanga/.gemini/oauth_creds.json) and [google_accounts.json](file:///C:/Users/tanga/.gemini/google_accounts.json) files were **ignored** for security.
You must **manually copy** these files from your Desktop's `.gemini` folder to your Notebook's `.gemini` folder, OR re-login on the notebook.

## 4. Syncing in the future
**On Desktop (after chatting):**
```powershell
cd C:\Users\tanga\.gemini
git add .
git commit -m "Sync conversations"
git push
```

**On Notebook (before chatting):**
```powershell
cd C:\Users\YOUR_USER\.gemini
git pull
```
